Cell["\<\
storing different tradeoff functions to try: 
tdoff[r_]:= -0.0001*Exp[3*r]
tdoff[r_]:= -0.0001 * b/(1 - b)
tdoff[r_]:=\[Minus]0.0000206*Exp[3.2*r]\
\>", "Text",
